831
00:44:05,757 --> 00:44:09,620
When evaluating design talent, the most important trait I look for is humility.

832
00:44:10,581 --> 00:44:15,124
Designers need to be able to hold two contradictory ideas in their heads at all times.

833
00:44:15,920 --> 00:44:17,341
to hold true to their design vision,

834
00:44:17,621 --> 00:44:18,902
even when success is uncertain,

835
00:44:19,422 --> 00:44:23,283
